Evertek bụ onye na-emepụta ekwentị na Tunisia

Evertek bụ akara ahịa nke Cellcom, nke n'aka nke ya bụ akụkụ nke ụlọ ọrụ Tunisia YKH Group. Malite na 2008, Evertek mepụtara ọtụtụ ekwentị mkpanaaka (Dual na triple SIM) ma na-enweta ọganihu na-aga n'ihu n'ahịa Tunisia.

N'ihe dị ka afọ 2010, ekwentị Evertek nwere òkè ahịa 10% na Tunisia, a na-erekwa ya na Morocco, France, na ụgbọ elu British Airways, KLM na Virgin Atlantic. Na Jenụwarị 2018, Evertek wepụtara smartphone V4 Nano. Na June nke afọ 2018, Evertek wepụtara smartphone ọhụrụ nke gam akporo V8 curved.
